Distribution. Mexico , Gulf of Mexico , Florida, Bahamas , Antilles, Cuba , Jamaica , Colombia , and Brazil (
Borrero-Pérez et al. 2002
; Alvarado 2011 ,
Solís-Marín et al. 2013
;
Martínez-Melo et al. 2015
). In Brazil from MA, PB, AL, BA, RJ, and SP ( Tommasi 1966a ; Kempf 1972 ;
Oliveira et al. 2010
; Smithsonian Database). In this study, we record the species for the first time from the coast of Ceará . From 110 to 2500 m (
Pawson et al. 2009
).
